## 10. Quality Guidance for Downstream Agents

- **demo-builder:** Build to spec, in section order, exactly as listed in
  Hero Feature. Do not invent extra sections or reorder. Treat the three data
  visualizations as first-class, fully coded, accessible components, not
  decorative filler. Wire the real backend for email capture; do not fake
  persistence client-side only.
- **CEO (pairs after this plan and after demo-builder):** Check spec
  fidelity above all else (right number of sections, right order, status
  pills present, two-column disclosure present, three-column partners
  present) and check that all three data visualizations are real/coded
  (not images, not third-party embeds) before passing.
- **proposal-writer:** Use the milestone plan in Section 8 verbatim for the
  timeline ask, state plainly that all three graphics are coded by Michael
  (to-apply ask 3), and bid $4,200 with the 40/40/20 milestone split unless
  Michael's notes say otherwise.
